        I'm sure many of you know about the <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2207"> Nitram's Collection Quest</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> aka activate the <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=10234">Xanamech Nexmirthafen</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> in POI.  Completing this quest flags your character to get inside the &quot;locked&quot; factory of the zone.  The dragon is not easy in fact he is quite difficult but the ends you could say justify the means his loot is quite nice considering the minimal risk involved.<br>
