Being that this is a PoP planar zone there will be no messy CR's just a simple rez in the graveyard.  The mob though is no pushover<br>
<br>
Can quad for 1390<br>
Has over 150K hp<br>
AOE slow<br>
He can be slowed<br>
<br>
The gist of the quest is we will walk the gnome vendor in POI to the dragon and the gnome will turn on the dragon for us to kill.  With several coordinated and balanced groups we can easily keep the gnome alive to get to the dragon.  The problem lies in learning how to handle the dragon and I believe that through a bit of trial and error we can figure this out and perhaps do him enough to equip the folks who want the loot as well as the character flag's.  Speaking as a warrior I know I would put off my epic indefinitely should I get my hands on the Cord Hilted Spike Driver, but that's just me.  I am inviting all friends and allies of House of November to take part in this adventure, hence why I have posted this on your forum.  <br>
<br>
Due to the difficulty and coordination required for a takedown of this size I would like to keep this event within the circle of friends and allies of HoN. <br>
<br>
I am going to set the level requirement on this at L57 with some leeway depending on class and what not, we are most certainly going to need two large well equipped tanks to take the beating and a solid group of clerics to perform a ch rotation, and a few folks capable of slowing the bad boy down.  <br>
<br>
At this time there is no set date, the goal is to gather enough friends together to do this and <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">then</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--> set the date.  The intent of this is to get the flags, get some nice loot, and most importantly have fun. <br>
